MyBroadband is the biggest ICT website in South Africa, and is home to the largest IT business and consumer audiences in the country. With over 2 million South Africans reading MyBroadband every month, it is the perfect place to make your ICT business stand out. To show you just how big MyBroadband is, we have compiled a list of seven amazing facts about the site below. MyBroadband received 21 million unique visitors and 100 million page views in 2019 – which was an all-time high for the publication. This makes it the biggest ICT publication in South Africa, and the leader in both the business and consumer ICT markets. In fact, 86% of MyBroadband’s readers advise their family and friends on which IT products and services to buy – while 61% of readers advise their company on which IT products to buy. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-294872" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/MyBroadband-Logo.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/MyBroadband-Logo.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/MyBroadband-Logo-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/MyBroadband-Logo-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> MyBroadband’s IT community and forum are legendary, with the forum hosting the most up-to-date and in-depth local technology discussions. The MyBroadband forum boasts over 13.5 million posts, 592,000 discussion topics, and 267,000 registered members. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-338368" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Typing-Laptop.jpg" alt="Typing Laptop" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Typing-Laptop.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Typing-Laptop-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroad